      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">30/7/94 ¶  ¶ Your sending of the names of many of the algae that came from Encounter Bay ¶  has pleased me greatly, noble friend, and a copy of the list was sent off at once to Miss Hussey ¶  as comin...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">94.07.30a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">30/7/94</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sehr erfreut hat mich Ihre Zusendung der Namen vieler der Algen, die von Encounter-Bay kamen, edler Freund, u ist sogleich eine Abschrift der Liste als von Ihnen kommend an Miss Hussey abgesandt, wodurch Selbige zum Weitersammeln wird ermuthigt werden. Manche der Arten sind mir durch eine lange Reihe Jahre bekannt, aber es ist ja doch am Besten, dass Sie das ganze Material zur Durchsicht bekommen, damit Ihnen auch von gewöhnlichen Arten die weitern Nachweise der Standorte bekannt werden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es ist nur gut, dass die göttliche Vorsehung Ihnen das Sehvermögen so erhält, dass Sie als Octogenar noch das Microscop gebrauchen können, was selbst bei Kützing nicht mehr möglich war.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Immer der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Würden Sie so freundlich sein bei dem Vertheilen der überzähligen Ex.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Exemplare.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> auch Paris zu bedenken id est Mons le Professeur Maxime Cornu</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30/7/94</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your sending of the names of many of the algae that came from Encounter Bay<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>SA.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> has pleased me greatly, noble friend, and a copy of the list was sent off at once to Miss Hussey<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="">Letter not found.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> as coming from you, by which she will be encouraged to further collecting. Several of the species are known to me over a long series of years, but it is of course best that you get all the material for examination, so that further information of the localities becomes known to you even of common species.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is good that Divine Providence preserves your vision so that as an octogenarian you can still use the microscope, which was no longer possible even with Kützing.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Would you be so kind with the distribution of superfluous specimens<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Distributed by Agardh under the title 'Algae Muellerianae'.</p>
               </note> to think also of Paris, that is Mons. le Professeur Maxime Cornu.</p>
         </div>
